<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/528> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #528" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Furius Fusus succeeded Servilius. ILS 9338, 2.- CIL 6.37161." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/526> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #526" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Furius Fusus succeeded Servilius. ILS 9338, 2.- CIL 6.37161." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/418> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #418" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Fast. Cap.; Liv. 4.46.10; Degrassi 26f., 97, 376f. Defeated the Aequi and captured Labici (Liv. 4.46.10-47.7; Frontin. Str. 2.8.8; cf. Diod. 13.6.7). See 435, Dictator." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/384> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #384" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Appointed to investigate the participation of Fidenates in Veientane raids (Liv. 4.30.5-6).{66}" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/351> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #351" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Captured Fidenae (Liv. 4.21.9-22.6; Frontin. Str. 2.8.8; Degrassi 95, 370f.)." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/350> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #350" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "On Servilius' name, see Fast. Cap. on 418. Livy has the praenomen A. and is uncertain whether the cognomen should be Priscus or Structus; but cf. 4.26.7, and 46.4." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/331> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #331" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "It is uncertain whether the fragment (ILS 9338, 3) refers to Pontiffs or Augurs since no. 3 refers to Augurs (see 40 B.C.) and no. 4 to Pontiffs (see 89 and 88). If the above identification is correct the omission of his grandfather's praenomen and his own cognomina are surprising (Dessau, loc. cit.). For the name, see Fast. Cap. on 418." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/330> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #330" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Q. Servilius succeeded Sp. Postumius.\n     ILS 9338, 2- CIL 6.37161.\n     On Postumius, see Lübker no. 17." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/329> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #329" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/2> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "It is uncertain whether the fragment (ILS 9338, 3) refers to Pontiffs or Augurs since no. 3 refers to Augurs (see 40 B.C.) and no. 4 to Pontiffs (see 89 and 88). If the above identification is correct the omission of his grandfather's praenomen and his own cognomina are surprising (Dessau, loc. cit.). For the name, see Fast. Cap. on 418." .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/328> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #328" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Q. Servilius succeeded Sp. Postumius.\n     ILS 9338, 2- CIL 6.37161.\n     On Postumius, see Lübker no. 17." .
